# 止蝕

(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue: 止蝕 嘅 事（量詞：個）
eng:to stop the damage

<eg>
yue: 我係止蝕，因為我唔好再跑。 (sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng:I am stopping the damage because I don't want to run.

<explanation>
yue: 止蝕 係 人 或 物 被 損壞 後 要 停止 動作 或 行為 嘅 詞。
eng:to stop the damage.

<eg>
yue: 我係止蝕，因為我唔好再跑。 (sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng:I am stopping the damage because I don't want to run. [end of text]


